'''土拉弗朗西斯菌'''（[[学名|学名]]：''{{lang|la|Francisella tularensis}}''），属于[[弗朗西斯菌属|弗朗西斯菌属]]，是一种[[專性需氧微生物|专性需氧]]、[[革兰氏阴性|革兰氏阴性]]的[[球杆菌|球杆菌]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Francisella tularensis|url=http://www.health.ny.gov/guidance/oph/wadsworth/francisella_tularensis.pdf|website=health.ny.gov|publisher=Wadsworth Center: New York State Department of Health|accessdate=12 May 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924025424/http://www.health.ny.gov/guidance/oph/wadsworth/francisella_tularensis.pdf|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。具多形性，无[[鞭毛|鞭毛]]，无[[运动性|运动性]]，不产生[[芽孢|芽孢]]，可产生[[荚膜|荚膜]]。该菌为[[兔热病|兔热病]]的病原体。因其{{tsl|en|Minimal infective dose|最小感染剂量}}低、[[毒性|毒性]]强、易发生[[气溶胶|气溶胶]]传播，故常用作[[生物武器|生物武器]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm6247a5.htm|title=Tularemia — United States, 2001–2010|website=www.cdc.gov|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200510093757/https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/preview/mmwrhtml/mm6247a5.htm|archive-date=2020-05-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=croddyhart>Croddy, Eric C. and Hart, C. Perez-Armendariz J., ''Chemical and Biological Warfare'', ([https://books.google.com/books?id=fGp53P6ijqsC&pg=PA30 Google Books] {{Wayback|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fGp53P6ijqsC&pg=PA30 |date=20200102224400 }}), Springer, 2002, pp. 30–31, ({{ISBN|0387950761}}), accessed October 24, 2008.</ref>。土拉弗朗西斯菌在外界环境中抵抗力较强，可在低温下于动物[[尸体|尸体]]、[[土壤|土壤]]和[[水|水]]中存活数週。该菌在实验室培养基上呈短杆状（0.2 x 0.2 µm），最适生长温度为37°C<ref>{{Cite web | url=https://microbewiki.kenyon.edu/index.php/Francisella_tularensis | title=Francisella tularensis – microbewiki | access-date=2020-07-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180913002359/https://microbewiki.kenyon.edu/index.php/Francisella_tularensis | archive-date=2018-09-13 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 生化鉴定 ==
[[革兰氏染色|革兰氏染色]]阴性，表现为两极染色。[[专性需氧菌|专性需氧]]。能[[乳酸发酵|乳酸发酵]][[葡萄糖|葡萄糖]]、[[果糖|果糖]]、[[甘露醇|甘露醇]]、[[甘油|甘油]]、[[麦芽糖|麦芽糖]]。不产生[[吲哚|靛基质]]。产生[[硫化氢|硫化氢]]。不[[硝酸盐还原酶|还原硝酸盐]]为[[亚硝酸盐|亚硝酸盐]]。普通[[培养基|培养基]]上必须添加[[半胱氨酸|半胱氨酸]]才能生长<ref name=Sherris>{{cite book | author = Ryan KJ; Ray CG (editors) | title = Sherris Medical Microbiology | edition = 4th | pages = 488–90 | publisher = McGraw Hill | year = 2004 | isbn = 0-8385-8529-9 }}</ref>。菌体能溶解于[[蓖麻酸|蓖麻酸]]等羟基酸中<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/chemistry/hydroxy-fatty-acid|title=Hydroxy Fatty Acid - an overview | ScienceDirect Topics|website=www.sciencedirect.com|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200716055426/https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/chemistry/hydroxy-fatty-acid}}</ref>。
