== 亚种 ==
[[1911年|1911年]]{{tsl|en|George Walter McCoy|麦考伊}}在[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[图莱里县|土拉县]]首次发现兔热病，并于[[1912年|1912年]]从[[黄鼠狼|黄鼠狼]]体内分离出该病的病原体，命名为'''土拉杆菌'''（''{{lang|la|Bacterium tularensis}}''），直至[[1970年|1970年]]{{tsl|en|International Committee on Systematic Bacteriology|国际系统细菌分类委员会}}正式定名为土拉弗朗西斯菌（''{{lang|la|Francisella tularensis}}''）<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://erj.ersjournals.com/content/21/2/361|title=Tularaemia|first1=A.|last1=Tärnvik|first2=L.|last2=Berglund|date=2003年2月1日|journal=European Respiratory Journal|volume=21|issue=2|pages=361–373|via=erj.ersjournals.com|doi=10.1183/09031936.03.00088903|pmid=12608453|author=|access-date=2020年7月16日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181028142839/http://erj.ersjournals.com/content/21/2/361|archive-date=2018年10月28日|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>McCoy GW, Chapin CW. Bacterium tularense, the cause of a plaguelike disease of rodents. Public Health Bull 1912;53:17–23.</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://history.nih.gov/research/downloads/Notable_Cont_Med_Research.pdf|title=Jeanette Barry, ''Notable Contributions to Medical Research by Public Health Service Scientists''. National Institute of Health, Public Health Service Publication No. 752, 1960, p. 36.|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190502013635/https://history.nih.gov/research/downloads/Notable_Cont_Med_Research.pdf|archive-date=2019-05-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

土拉弗朗西斯菌在地理上可分型为2个[[亚种|亚种]]：

*美洲亚种（{{lang|en|''F. t.'' subsp. ''tularensis''}}；A型菌）主要分布于[[北美|北美]]，毒性较强，导致致命的[[肺炎|肺部感染]]<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3372352/|title=Real-time PCR for Francisella tularensis Types A and B|first1=Kiersten J.|last1=Kugeler|first2=Ryan|last2=Pappert|first3=Yan|last3=Zhou|first4=Jeannine M.|last4=Petersen|date=2006年11月16日|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|volume=12|issue=11|pages=1799–1801|via=PubMed Central|doi=10.3201/eid1211.060629|pmid=17283646|pmc=3372352}}</ref>。
*欧洲亚种（{{lang|en|''F. t.'' subsp. ''holarctica''}}；B型菌）主要分布于[[欧洲|欧洲]]和[[亚洲|亚洲]]，毒性较弱，很少致命<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC3310461/|title=Phylogeography of Francisella tularensis subsp. holarctica, Europe|first1=Miklós|last1=Gyuranecz|first2=Dawn N.|last2=Birdsell|first3=Wolf|last3=Splettstoesser|first4=Erik|last4=Seibold|first5=Stephen M.|last5=Beckstrom-Sternberg|first6=László|last6=Makrai|first7=László|last7=Fodor|first8=Massimo|last8=Fabbi|first9=Nadia|last9=Vicari|first10=Anders|last10=Johansson|first11=Joseph D.|last11=Busch|first12=Amy J.|last12=Vogler|first13=Paul|last13=Keim|first14=David M.|last14=Wagner|date=2012年2月16日|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|volume=18|issue=2|pages=290–293|via=PubMed Central|doi=10.3201/eid1802.111305|pmid=22305204|pmc=3310461}}</ref>。

两个地理亚种的[[免疫原性|免疫原性]]不同<ref name=Larsson_2005>{{cite journal | author = Larsson P | title = The complete genome sequence of ''Francisella tularensis'', the causative agent of tularemia | journal = Nat Genet | volume = 37 | issue = 2 | pages = 153–9 | year = 2005 | pmid = 15640799 | doi = 10.1038/ng1499 |name-list-format=vanc| author2 = Oyston P | author3 = Chain P | display-authors = 3 | last4 = Chu | first4 = May C | last5 = Duffield | first5 = Melanie | last6 = Fuxelius | first6 = Hans-Henrik | last7 = Garcia | first7 = Emilio | last8 = Hälltorp | first8 = Greger | last9 = Johansson | first9 = Daniel}}</ref>。土拉弗朗西斯菌含有2种主要[[抗原|抗原]]，即[[表面抗原|表面抗原]]和荚膜抗原（Vi抗原）<ref name="SpidlovaStulik2017">{{cite journal|last1=Spidlova|first1=Petra|last2=Stulik|first2=Jiri|title=Francisella tularensis type VI secretion system comes of age|journal=Virulence|volume=8|issue=6|year=2017|pages=628–631|issn=2150-5594|doi=10.1080/21505594.2016.1278336|pmid=28060573|pmc=5626347}}</ref>。Vi抗原与毒性和免疫原性有关，丧失Vi抗原的菌株失去毒性和免疫原性。土拉弗朗西斯菌和[[布魯氏桿菌病|布鲁氏菌]]有共同抗原成分<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://iai.asm.org/cgi/reprint/76/8/3690 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-date=2020-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200307165222/https://iai.asm.org/content/iai/76/8/3690.full.pdf }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/|title=Wiley Online Library|website=Wiley Online Library|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200317064012/https://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/|archive-date=2020-03-17|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Atkins_2006>{{cite journal |vauthors=Atkins H, Dassa E, Walker N, Griffin K, Harland D, Taylor R, Duffield M, Titball R | title = The identification and evaluation of ATP binding cassette systems in the intracellular bacterium ''Francisella tularensis'' | journal = Res Microbiol | volume = 157 | issue = 6 | pages = 593–604 | year = 2006| pmid = 16503121 | doi = 10.1016/j.resmic.2005.12.004}}</ref>。

== 流行病学 ==
[[File:Amblyomma_americanum_tick_2.jpg|thumb]]是土拉弗朗西斯菌的自然宿主]]
土拉弗朗西斯菌主要分布在30°N以北。对该菌易感的动物种类很多，包括许多[[脊椎动物|脊椎动物]]，如[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]、[[鸟类|鸟类]]、[[鱼类|鱼类]]、[[蛙类|蛙类]]和[[蟾蜍|蟾蜍]]；[[无脊椎动物|无脊椎动物]]，如[[蜱|蜱]]、[[蚊|蚊]]、[[虻|虻]]、[[蚤|蚤]]、[[螨|螨]]和一些[[双翅目|双翅目]][[吸血_(生物学)|吸血动物]]；[[两栖动物|两栖动物]]和[[软体动物|软体动物]]等也可感染<ref name="agent">{{Cite web |url=http://clsjournal.ascls.org/content/ascls/17/1/35.full.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200320080317/http://clsjournal.ascls.org/content/ascls/17/1/35.full.pdf |archive-date=2020-03-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK7798/|title=Pasteurella, Yersinia, and Francisella|first=Frank M.|last=Collins|editor-first=Samuel|editor-last=Baron|date=1996年7月16日|publisher=University of Texas Medical Branch at Galveston|via=PubMed|pmid=21413268|access-date=2020年7月16日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200530022848/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK7798/|archive-date=2020年5月30日|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="hypersensitivity">{{Cite web|url=https://www.webmd.com/a-to-z-guides/what-is-tularemia|title=What Is Tularemia?|website=WebMD|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-date=2022-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220323201203/https://www.webmd.com/a-to-z-guides/what-is-tularemia}}</ref>。

[[野兔|野兔]]和其他[[啮齿动物|啮齿动物]]是主要传染源。其他[[野生动物|野生动物]]、[[家畜|家畜]]和[[家禽|家禽]]感染后，也能成为传染源。其自然宿主包括[[蜱虫|蜱虫]]、[[蚊子|蚊子]]和鹿蝇等。该菌在蜱虫体内可存活数年，且能通过[[卵|卵]]传递给下一代<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.merckmanuals.com/home/infections/bacterial-infections-gram-negative-bacteria/tularemia|title=Tularemia - Infections|website=Merck Manuals Consumer Version|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200211132017/https://www.merckmanuals.com/home/infections/bacterial-infections-gram-negative-bacteria/tularemia|archive-date=2020-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="agent"/>。

土拉弗朗西斯菌感染可通过多种途径发生，主要通过吸血[[节肢动物|节肢动物]]叮咬而传播，也可经由[[皮肤|皮肤]]和[[黏膜|黏膜]]的伤口而感染。此外，还可通过[[粪口路径|粪口路径]]感染、经[[呼吸道|呼吸道]]和[[消化道|消化道]]感染等<ref>{{Cite journal|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC5934503/|title=Single vector platform vaccine protects against lethal respiratory challenge with Tier 1 select agents of anthrax, plague, and tularemia|first1=Qingmei|last1=Jia|first2=Richard|last2=Bowen|first3=Barbara Jane|last3=Dillon|first4=Saša|last4=Masleša-Galić|first5=Brennan T.|last5=Chang|first6=Austin C.|last6=Kaidi|first7=Marcus A.|last7=Horwitz|date=2018年5月3日|journal=Scientific Reports|volume=8|via=PubMed Central|doi=10.1038/s41598-018-24581-y|pmid=29725025|pmc=5934503}}</ref><ref name="agent"/>。

该菌能在[[宿主|宿主]]体外存活数週，常发现于[[天然水|天然水]]、[[土壤|土壤]]和[[干草堆|干草堆]]中<ref name="agent"/>。

== 生命週期 ==
土拉弗朗西斯菌是一种[[細胞內寄生物#兼性寄生物|兼性细胞内寄生菌]]，其生长与繁殖依靠宿主细胞。土拉弗朗西斯菌可感染大多数种类的细胞，但主要感染[[巨噬细胞|巨噬细胞]]。土拉弗朗西斯菌经由[[吞噬作用|吞噬作用]]进入巨噬细胞并迅速增殖，最终受感染细胞[[凋亡|凋亡]]并释放子代细菌，引发新一轮感染<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Carruthers|first=Jonathan|last2=Lythe|first2=Grant|last3=López-García|first3=Martín|last4=Gillard|first4=Joseph|last5=Laws|first5=Thomas R.|last6=Lukaszewski|first6=Roman|last7=Molina-París|first7=Carmen|date=2020-06-01|title=Stochastic dynamics of Francisella tularensis infection and replication|url=https://journals.plos.org/ploscompbiol/article?id=10.1371/journal.pcbi.1007752|journal=PLOS Computational Biology|language=en|volume=16|issue=6|pages=e1007752|doi=10.1371/journal.pcbi.1007752|issn=1553-7358|author=|access-date=2020-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200612142631/https://journals.plos.org/ploscompbiol/article?id=10.1371%2Fjournal.pcbi.1007752|archive-date=2020-06-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 诊断、治疗及预防 ==
[[File:Francisella_tularensis_01.jpg|thumb]]上生长的土拉弗朗西斯菌菌落]]
=== 诊断 ===
通常根据症状和患者[[病史|病史]]、[[医学造影|医学造影]]和化验来诊断该病。亦可经由[[变态反应|变态反应]]加以诊断。

=== 治疗 ===
土拉弗朗西斯菌对[[链霉素|链霉素]]、[[四环素|四环素]]和[[氯霉素|氯霉素]]等[[抗生素|抗生素]]敏感，也可用[[土霉素|土霉素]]、[[金霉素|金霉素]]、[[庆大霉素|庆大霉素]]等治疗。此外，根据病情可采用[[对症治疗|对症治疗]]<ref>Francisella tularensis: ''In silico'' Identification of Drug and Vaccine Targets by Metabolic Pathway Analysis
J Harati, J Fallah
The 6th Conference on Bioinformatics</ref>。

=== 预防 ===
预防措施包括防止蜱虫、鹿蝇和蚊子叮咬；彻底煮熟[[野味|野味]]；不饮未经[[水处理|处理]]的水；避免接触疫源动物；用冻干弱毒菌苗[[预防接种|预防接种]]，可保持免疫力数年。此外，土拉弗朗西斯菌对热和化学药物敏感，一般消毒剂均能很快将其杀死<ref name="hypersensitivity"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://publichealth.lacounty.gov/acd/procs/b73/B73Part4.pdf |title=存档副本 |access-date=2020-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921012050/http://publichealth.lacounty.gov/acd/procs/b73/B73Part4.pdf |archive-date=2018-09-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

